room_title: Escape room "Escape the Roxbury" by Green Light Escape Room in Wilmington
review: Went with friends to do the Escape from the Roxbury... so much fun! Totally made my birthday weekend a smash!

room_title: Escape room "Escape the Roxbury" by Green Light Escape Room in Wilmington
review: A very fun experience! We did the “Night at the Roxbury” room. Will definitely return next time we’re in the area to try a different room!

room_title: Escape room "Escape the Roxbury" by Green Light Escape Room in Wilmington
review: We did "The Roxbury Room" and had a fantastic time. It was well laid out, challenging, and one of the best escape rooms yet! If you want a fun team room this one is highly recommend!
